### 6. Criar Evento (somente admin)
### =======================

POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Campanha de Doação de Sangue",
  "description": "Doe sangue e salve vidas",
  "date": "2025-10-25",
  "location": "Campus Central",
  "max_volunteers": 100
}

###

POST http://localhost:3000/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{VOLUNTEER_TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Tentativa Usuário Comum",
  "description": "Não deve funcionar",
  "date": "2025-10-30",
  "location": "Campus Secundário",
  "max_volunteers": 50
}

